ATTRIBUTION REQUIREMENT FOR GT3N FORGE CONTRIBUTIONS

When using a GT3N Forge contribution under this license, attribution should
include:

  - Builder handle (as listed on the GT3N Forge Wall of Records)
  - Mission title and GT3N project
  - Link to the original Wall of Records entry (when GT3N Forge is publicly
    deployed)
  - This license notice

Example attribution format:

  "[Output title]" by [Builder Handle], contributed via GT3N Forge for
  [Project Name]. Licensed under CC BY 4.0.
  https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/
